{
  "id": "69b0847ab7bd510eb8c6100d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:黒歴史との向き合い方",
  "created": 1773175957,
  "updated": 1773175973,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b0847ab7bd510eb8c6100d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:黒歴史との向き合い方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175957,
      "updated": 1773175957
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08495000000000047d9ae",
      "text": "[黒歴史]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175957,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9af",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b1",
      "text": "やっほー、今日は「黒歴史との向き合い方」ってテーマでゆるく話していくよ～！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b2",
      "text": "黒歴史ってさ、あるじゃん？　昔の自分の行動とか発言とか思い出して「うわあああ！」ってなるやつ。深夜テンションのポエムとか、謎のキャラ設定ノートとか……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b3",
      "text": "うちも普通にある。マジである。消したいログいっぱいある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b5",
      "text": "というわけで！　二人はどう？　黒歴史、ある派？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b8",
      "text": "ええ……ございますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9b9",
      "text": "誰しもの胸の奥に、そっとしまわれた小箱のようなものが。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9bb",
      "text": "わたくしの場合は、そうですね……中学生のころ、たいへん重々しい恋愛詩を書いておりました。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9bc",
      "text": "「月は私の涙を知っている」などと……今思えば、ずいぶん大仰でしたわね。（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9be",
      "text": "でも、不思議と嫌いではないのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9bf",
      "text": "あの頃のわたくしは、あれでも真剣だったのですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c1",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c2",
      "text": "黒歴史。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c3",
      "text": "定義を簡潔に言うと、「現在の自己評価と整合しない過去の行動や表現」だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c5",
      "text": "心理学では、自己概念の更新によって過去の自己が恥ずかしく感じられる現象として説明されることが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c6",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c7",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-concept",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9c9",
      "text": "つまり、黒歴史があるということは、自己モデルがアップデートされた証拠。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ca",
      "text": "ソフトウェアで言えば旧バージョンのログ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9cc",
      "text": "消す必要はない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9cd",
      "text": "むしろデバッグ資料。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9cf",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d0",
      "text": "デバッグ資料ｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d1",
      "text": "黒歴史＝デバッグログってこと！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d3",
      "text": "いやでもちょっとわかるかも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d4",
      "text": "昔のSNSとか見返すと、「なんでこんなこと書いたんだ自分」ってなるけど、同時に「当時マジでそれ好きだったんだなー」ってのも見えるし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d6",
      "text": "でもさ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d7",
      "text": "問題は思い出した瞬間に「うわあああ！」ってなることなんだよ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d8",
      "text": "あの精神ダメージどうすんの！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9da",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9db",
      "text": "それは認知的不協和に近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9dc",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cognitive_dissonance",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9de",
      "text": "現在の自分の価値観と、過去の行動が衝突する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9df",
      "text": "脳は「エラー」を検出する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e1",
      "text": "対処法は大きく三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e2",
      "text": " 1. 過去を再解釈する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e3",
      "text": " 2. 経験として統合する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e4",
      "text": " 3. ネタ化する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e5",
      "text": "特に3は有効。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e6",
      "text": "羞恥の社会的リフレーミング。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9e9",
      "text": "ネタ化ｗｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ea",
      "text": "それネット民の基本スキルじゃん！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ec",
      "text": "「昔こんな黒歴史あってさ～ｗ」って自分から言うやつね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ed",
      "text": "先に自分で笑うことでダメージ減らすテク。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ef",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f0",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f1",
      "text": "それは、なんだか舞台のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f3",
      "text": "自分の過去を、少し離れたところから眺めて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f4",
      "text": "「こんな役を演じておりました」と語る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f6",
      "text": "そうすると、その頃の自分も、どこか愛おしく思えてまいります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f8",
      "text": "たとえ拙くても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9f9",
      "text": "あの時のわたくしは、精いっぱい生きていたのだと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9fa",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9fc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9fd",
      "text": "いい表現だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047d9ff",
      "text": "補足すると、これは心理的距離の確保。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da00",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychological_distance",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da02",
      "text": "過去の自分を「別の人物」として観察すると、羞恥や後悔が弱くなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da04",
      "text": "要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da05",
      "text": "黒歴史との向き合い方：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da06",
      "text": " 成長のログと認識する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da07",
      "text": " 視点を離して観察する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da08",
      "text": " 可能ならネタ化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da09",
      "text": "この3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0c",
      "text": "なんかさ、聞いてて思ったんだけど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0e",
      "text": "黒歴史って「恥ずかしい記憶」じゃなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da0f",
      "text": "レベル1の自分のプレイログみたいなもんじゃない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da11",
      "text": "ゲームでもさ、最初のプレイってミスだらけじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da12",
      "text": "でもそれないとレベル上がらんし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da14",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da15",
      "text": "まあ……それは、とても素敵なたとえですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da17",
      "text": "人の成長も、物語のようなものですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da18",
      "text": "第一章の主人公は、まだ未熟で、少し滑稽で……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da19",
      "text": "けれど、その歩みがあるからこそ、物語は続いていく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1b",
      "text": "黒歴史とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1c",
      "text": "物語の最初のページなのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1e",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da1f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da20",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da21",
      "text": "結論をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da22",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da23",
      "text": "黒歴史は削除対象ではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da24",
      "text": "履歴データ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da26",
      "text": "むしろ問題は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da27",
      "text": "黒歴史が「存在しない人」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da29",
      "text": "それは更新停止の可能性が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2c",
      "text": "おお、なんか急にラスボス感あるまとめ来たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2e",
      "text": "つまり今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da30",
      "text": "黒歴史＝成長ログ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da31",
      "text": "思い出して「うわあああ！」ってなったら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da32",
      "text": "「お、レベル上がってるじゃん自分」って思えばOK！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da34",
      "text": "……まあ、それでも夜に思い出すとダメージ来るけどね！！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da35",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da36",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da37",
      "text": "そのときは、温かいお茶でも飲んで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da38",
      "text": "「昔のわたくしも頑張っていたのですね」と、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da39",
      "text": "そっと許してあげればよろしいのではないでしょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3c",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3e",
      "text": "ログは残る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da3f",
      "text": "だが、プログラムは更新され続ける。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da41",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da42",
      "text": "なんか最後ちょっとカッコよく終わった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da44",
      "text": "じゃあ今日はこのへんで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da45",
      "text": "黒歴史に苦しむみんな、安心してくれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08496000000000047da47",
      "text": "それ、成長の証だぞ！ ✌️",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175958,
      "updated": 1773175958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0849a000000000047da48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175962,
      "updated": 1773175962
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0849b000000000047da49",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175963,
      "updated": 1773175973
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0849c000000000047da4a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773175965,
      "updated": 1773175965
    }
  ]
}